    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "flakes are bad 2 two reasons:\r\n\r\n1. maybe there is a bug in our code that is the underlying cause of the flake\r\n2. developers rerun the tests and get used to ignoring test failures\r\n\r\nIf we can't prioritize immediately investigating and fixing the issue (i.e. point 1 above doesn't worry us very much), we should disable the test to avoid point 2.",
